org.springframework.geode.boot.autoconfigure.configuration.support

Class PeerSecurityProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.geode.boot.autoconfigure.configuration.support.PeerSecurityProperties

  • public class PeerSecurityProperties
extends java.lang.Object
    Spring Boot ConfigurationProperties used to configure an Apache Geode peer Cache Security (authentication & authorization). The configuration Properties are based on well-known, documented Spring Data for Apache Geode (SDG) Properties.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    See Also:
    Properties, Cache, ConfigurationProperties
